{"tid":815333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣10.1遊行　狙擊港鐵淪陷","createTime":"2018-09-12T03:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T12:24:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a395527260fa250b3d803e81578e82ff90193002","tid":815333,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:38:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180912/20497495\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180912%2F20497495&d=0ae027bs3124tcF0V6cgnAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=fb23c39b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180912%2F20497495&h=ff6209d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180912/20497495</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月12日 <br />\n<br />\n民陣10.1遊行　狙擊港鐵淪陷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180912/large/0911yik4001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180912%2Flarge%2F0911yik4001.jpg&h=cf549b7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民間人權陣線將於10月1日發起「拒絕危城」遊行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵沙中綫醜聞越演越烈，但至今卻未有官員因此問責下台。民間人權陣線將於10月1日發起「拒絕危城」遊行，要求徹查沙中綫問題、主責的運房局局長陳帆問責下台，並質疑「沒有安全國家，談何國家安全」。民陣召集人葉志衍表示無論參與人數多寡都會遊行，拒絕讓政府以為社會歌舞昇平，以為沒有反對聲音。<br />\n<br />\n民陣昨日聯同多個民主派政團舉行記者會，宣佈在今年10月1日下午3時發起遊行，遊行後會將在政總公民廣場舉行集會。民陣已就遊行向警方申請不反對通知書，預計人數約2,000人，他們相信獲批不反對通知書的機會相當大。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉小麗籲拯救香港制度<br />\n<br />\n葉志衍稱，即使港鐵多名高層請辭，但政府至今未有官員問責下台，故發起遊行拒絕令香港變成「危城」，民陣同時會在本周發起狙擊建制派，不滿他們放生政府，並邀特首林鄭月娥就沙中綫對話。遊行同時亦會表達對政府擬以《公安條例》取締民族黨的不滿和拒絕《基本法》23條立法的立場。<br />\n<br />\n參與遊行的劉小麗指，沙中綫問題反映了香港制度的漏洞、體制的崩壞，今次的遊行不止爭取鐵路安全，同時要求徹查事件真相，她呼籲市民參與「拯救香港嘅制度」。專業議政、社福界議員邵家臻指，沙中綫事件反映用人唯親，專業淪陷，呼籲專業人士遊行。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n站外車禍演習　近百人出動"},{"pid":"5ba204e34c0f481bf54bc29aa8073f224e1adb1f","tid":815333,"uid":202464,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:41:25.000Z","msg":"遊行還有用嗎？"},{"pid":"48f807fd3169184d25a8fb4bc5bbe6bbfdb6ff06","tid":815333,"uid":1221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:44:32.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"ce028a758e903966b4c0ced4efd932fefec8952d","tid":815333,"uid":12021,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:28:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2aa2dc46112c5e5e316dd74e7808c2f71e160429","tid":815333,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:29:41.000Z","msg":"樓上巴打咁勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb05043e1f3b265e9b14355732950f7f6a774ab","tid":815333,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:20:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d047f2fbda69a15963f81c45a7d8ce6dbdd31cc8","tid":815333,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T09:17:13.000Z","msg":"我唔想生命有事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8b965b978a47d55e92ef109432b4a81b500201","tid":815333,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T09:19:50.000Z","msg":"啱啱打完風都唔識食住個勢<br />\n拿拿淋改番個標題，大把人出黎行啦"},{"pid":"d8f7bb4f9561a47150d479bde728bdf99bfa6933","tid":815333,"uid":62226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce028a758e903966b4c0ced4efd932fefec8952d","tid":815333,"uid":12021,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:28:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T09:24:34.000Z","msg":"星期六通車禮冇話有咩搞作<br />\n星期日通車都冇聲氣<br />\n<br />\n唔通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br 